    • Constructor Detail

      • ItemOrder

        public ItemOrder(Item item,
                 int quantity,
                 java.lang.String notes)
        A constructor of the ItemOrder object. It sets the item id, name and description that represents, as well as its quantity and any extra notes. The order that it belongs is set to -1.
        Parameters:
        item - the item that represents.
        quantity - the quantity of that item in the order.
        notes - any extra notes for that item.

      • ItemOrder

        public ItemOrder(java.util.Vector<java.lang.Object> vec)
        A constructor of the ItemOrder object for report creation. It reads a vector that was returned from JDBC in order to construct the object as it is on the database.
        Parameters:
        vec - a vector that is returned from JDBC
